<pb ed="ZW" xml:id="ZW07.0059b.0061a" n="0061a"/>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0061a01"/><milestone unit="juan" n="1"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">錄文二</cb:mulu><head>〔錄文二〕</head>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0061a02"/>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0061a03"/><cb:juan fun="open" n="1"><cb:mulu type="卷" n="1"/><cb:jhead>金剛五禮<note n="0061001" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">底本在「金剛五禮」前有「已後是」三字，據甲本刪。</note></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0061a04"/>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0061a05"/><p xml:id="pZW07p0061a0501" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">一心敬<note n="0061002" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「敬」，甲本作「滿敬」。</note>禮，清淨真如，無去無來，不生不滅，
<lb ed="ZW" n="0061a06"/>寂<note n="0061003" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「寂」，底本作「湛」，據甲本改。</note>然常住，坦<note n="0061004" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「坦」，甲本無。</note>矣<note n="0061005" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「矣」，甲本作「意」。</note>恒安，千佛共遵<note n="0061006" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「遵」，甲本作「尊」。</note>，十方同敬，恒
<lb ed="ZW" n="0061a07"/>沙功德，非色非心<note n="0061007" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「非色非心」，底本無，據甲本補。</note>，南無清淨法身毗盧遮那佛。</p>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0061a08"/><p xml:id="pZW07p0061a0801" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">一心敬禮，毗盧遮那，千葉蓮花，四智珍寶，
<lb ed="ZW" n="0061a09"/>德山無極，願海無邊，積行三祇，累功十地，光<note n="0061008" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「光」，甲本作「廣」。</note>充<note n="0061009" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「充」，甲本作「超」。</note>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0061a10"/>法界，體滿虛空，南無圓滿報身盧舍那佛。</p>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0061a11"/><p xml:id="pZW07p0061a1101" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">一心敬禮，如來生地，雪山之<note n="0061010" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「之」，甲本作「至」。</note>北，香山之東，
<lb ed="ZW" n="0061a12"/>城號加維，姓<note n="0061011" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「姓」，底本作「性」，甲本無，據伯3664號改。</note>釋迦氏<note n="0061012" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「釋迦氏」，甲本無。</note>，父名淨飯，母曰<note n="0061013" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「曰」，甲本作「號」。</note>摩耶，十
<lb ed="ZW" n="0061a13"/>九出家，三十<note n="0061014" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「三十」，底本作「卅」，據甲本改。</note>成道，南無千百億化身釋<note n="0061015" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「釋」，甲本作「同名釋」。</note>迦牟尼佛。</p>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0061a14"/><p xml:id="pZW07p0061a1401" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">一心敬禮，甚深微妙，金剛般若<note n="0061016" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「甚深微妙，金剛般若」，甲本作「金剛般若，微妙甚深」。「甚」，底本作「深」，據文意改。</note>，不可思議<note n="0062001" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「不可思議」，甲本無。「議」，底本作「儀」，據伯3664號改。</note>，
<pb ed="ZW" xml:id="ZW07.0059b.0062a" n="0062a"/>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0062a01"/>生諸佛身，滅凡夫罪，無人無我，聲空色空，苦惱
<lb ed="ZW" n="0062a02"/>蓋纏，因此<note n="0062002" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「此」，甲本作「茲」。</note>永寂<note n="0062003" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「寂」，底本作「息」，據甲本改。</note>，南無般<note n="0062004" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「般」，甲本作「金剛般」。</note>若波羅蜜多甚<note n="0062005" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「甚」，底本作「深」，據甲本改。</note>深法藏。</p>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0062a03"/><p xml:id="pZW07p0062a0301" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">一心敬禮，舍衛城南<note n="0062006" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「舍衛城南」，底本作「如來精舍」，據甲本改。</note>，須達園中，祇陀林下，
<lb ed="ZW" n="0062a04"/>如來精舍<note n="0062007" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「精舍」，底本作「說法」，據甲本改。</note>，聖眾禪房，於彼<note n="0062008" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「彼」，甲本作「此」。</note>伽藍<note n="0062009" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「伽藍」，甲本無。</note>，說斯<note n="0062010" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「斯」，底本作「思」，據甲本改。</note>般若，我
<lb ed="ZW" n="0062a05"/>今恭<note n="0062011" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「恭」，底本作「共」，據甲本改。</note>敬，追<note n="0062012" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「追」，甲本作「憶」。</note>念世尊，南無般<note n="0062013" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「般」，甲本作「金剛般」。</note>若波羅蜜多甚<note n="0062014" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「甚」，底本作「深」，據甲本改。</note>深法
<lb ed="ZW" n="0062a06"/>藏<note n="0062015" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「藏」，甲本於此後有「竟」字。</note>。</p>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0062a07"/>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0062a08"/><p xml:id="pZW07p0062a0801">〔錄文完〕</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0062a09"/>
<lb ed="ZW" n="0062a10"/><cb:div type="w"><p xml:id="pZW07p0062a1001" rend="margin-left:8em">（方廣錩修訂終審）</p></cb:div>
</body></text></TEI>